# Notely

An AngularJS 1.x note-taking app.

## Setup

__Install [MongoDB](https://www.mongodb.org/downloads#production)__:

    $ brew install mongodb
    $ mongod

__Clone [this project](https://github.com/unixmonkey/caedence.net-2015)__:

    $ git clone https://github.com/unixmonkey/caedence.net-2015.git notely


__Change into the `notely` directory and run `npm start` to start the server process__:

    $ cd notely
    $ npm start

__Open a new terminal tab/window, change into the notely `client` directory and run `npm start` to start the client build/watch process__:

    $ cd client
    $ npm start

__Open your web browser to [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)__
